OL,3,CBank holds interest rates and warns of
OL,4,Crising unemployment and weak growth
OL,6,FInflation stood at 3.4% in December,
OL,7,Fwith suggestions that the Bank of
OL,8,FEngland's target of 2% could be
OL,9,Freached by April. ITV News Economics
OL,10,FEditor Joel Hills reports
OL,12,FThe Bank of England says inflation
OL,13,Flooks set to fade faster than it had
OL,14,Fpreviously forecast, thanks in large
OL,15,Fpart to the chancellor's Budget, but
OL,16,Fwarns it's still too soon to declare
OL,17,Fvictory.
