OL,3,CBank holds interest rates and warns of
OL,4,Crising unemployment and weak growth
OL,6,FThe Bank calculates that the discount
OL,7,Fon energy bills - worth #134 a year to
OL,8,Fthe average household - announced by
OL,9,Fthe government last November, combined
OL,10,Fwith a temporary freeze to rail fares,
OL,11,Fwill help to drag the headline annual
OL,12,Frate of Consumer Price inflation down
OL,13,Fby 0.5 percentage points in April -
OL,14,Fback to within a whisker of its 2%
OL,15,Ftarget by April. And the expectation
OL,16,Fis it's likely to stay there.
OL,18,F"That's good news," says Andrew
OL,19,FBailey, Governor of the Bank of
OL,20,FEngland.
