OL,3,CBank holds interest rates and warns of
OL,4,Crising unemployment and weak growth
OL,6,F"We need to make sure that inflation
OL,7,Fstays there, so we've held rates
OL,8,Funchanged at 3.75% today. All going
OL,9,Fwell, there should be scope for some
OL,10,Ffurther reduction in Bank Rate this
OL,11,Fyear."
OL,13,FThe Monetary Policy Committee (MPC) -
OL,14,Fthe nine men and women who set the
OL,15,Fcost of borrowing - voted five to four
OL,16,Fto hold. That's close.
