OL,3,CBank holds interest rates and warns of
OL,4,Crising unemployment and weak growth
OL,6,FThe chancellor's Budget support is
OL,7,Ftemporary, and some on the MPC are
OL,8,Fconcerned that inflation could take
OL,9,Foff again when it ends - not least
OL,10,Fbecause they judge pay growth to be
OL,11,Funcomfortably high and some prices to
OL,12,Fbe still unstable.
OL,14,FBut some on the MPC wanted to cut now.
OL,15,FThey view the weakness of both the
OL,16,Feconomy and the labour market as a
OL,17,Fgreater concern.
