OL,3,CBank holds interest rates and warns of
OL,4,Crising unemployment and weak growth
OL,6,FThere has been a rapid and striking
OL,7,Frise in unemployment in the last year.
OL,8,FThe number of people who are looking
OL,9,Ffor work has climbed from 1.5 million
OL,10,Fto 1.8 million, and the Bank thinks
OL,11,Fthe level will edge up further,
OL,12,Fpeaking above 1.9 million.
OL,14,FThe number of redundancies has risen
OL,15,Fslightly in Britain, but the Bank says
OL,16,Fthe main issue is a reluctance to
OL,17,Frecruit.
