OL,6,FBusinesses are telling the Bank's
OL,7,Fagents they are increasingly likely to
OL,8,Fexplore the use of Artificial
OL,9,FIntelligence instead of hiring, and
OL,10,Fthey report that the cost of employing
OL,11,Fsomeone has risen significantly due to
OL,12,Fthe increases in national insurance
OL,13,Fand the minimum wage, announced in the
OL,14,Fchancellor's first Budget.
