OL,3,CBank holds interest rates and warns of
OL,4,Crising unemployment and weak growth
OL,6,FThe Bank points out the world economy
OL,7,Fhas proved resilient to the trade
OL,8,Fupheaval US President Donald Trump
OL,9,Finitiated, but it thinks the UK
OL,10,Feconomy will only grow by 0.9% in 2026
OL,11,F- less than the 1.2% predicted three
OL,12,Fmonths ago.
OL,14,FGrowth is subdued, and unemployment is
OL,15,Fedging up. In different circumstances,
OL,16,Fyou'd expect the central bank to be
OL,17,Freducing the cost of borrowing in an
OL,18,Feffort to encourage businesses and
OL,19,Fhouseholds to spend and invest.
